Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,an aspect of consciousness itself\Nuh presents a paradox
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,because 600 isn't the solution of every\Nparadox that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Um and a paradox will appear and with it\Nthis racking physical pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,uh one then intuitits what the paradox\Nis or it just comes to you as you're
