Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,extremely abstract and which are not\Nreally worth bothering bothering with
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,for the average person.\NThose of you know know my personal story
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:17:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,know that\Nwhich I recounted in the back of power
