Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the eye um this particular sojurnn\Nspiritual sojurn standing here talking
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to you began at age three went out as\Ncomplete nothingness suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a shocking awareness of\Nexistence
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,not pleasing either\Nsuddenly where there was a shock
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,shocking awareness of existence\Nhad returned into actual existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh the paradox then that arose at age\Nthree there was no mentation but there
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,was a complete and total understanding\Nof the paradox.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There came the fear of non-existence\Nto exist brings up its polar opposite of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,non-existence and the fear came up. If I\Nhad come into existence then it might
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,have been that I would not have come\Ninto existence. So the paradox to be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,solved in this lifetime which only took\Nanother 50 years to solve or something
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,uh or 60 years whatever uh was existence\Nversus non-existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That paradox to solve that paradox takes\Nyou beyond what let's see what what
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,existence versus non-existence is.\NExistence versus non-existence comes up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,uh as a blockade at 800, 810, 840,\N8:30, 8:35. It comes up at 8:35. So a
