Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that paradox of existence versus\Nnon-existence, it's really
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the question is really is there an\Nopposite to God? And the answer is no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there an opposite to existence? No.\NSo it's a very high paradox. But you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:19:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have to worry about it until then.\NThat's the good news. But um the bad
