Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,after having reached such a blissful\Nstate, you go through some agonizing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,states. We were in Korea and uh I was in\Nsuch an agonizing state. I forget what
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that polarity was. U\Nyou see consciousness is is blocked all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the time by a positionality which we'll\Nget into. Positionality creates a
