Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,all that which everybody's familiar\Nwith. But there are paradoxical
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,seeming dualities\Nat much higher levels. But you don't
