Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,painful. It's like it's like your whole\Nbody's on fire. It's like your nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,system is made up of barbed wire and the\Nbarbed wire has now has electricity
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,running through it and it's a racked\Npain. It's really within the whole aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get away from it because it's\Nthe aura that does that. So this demand,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in other words, it demands attention.\NSo uh
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was questioning why that is or\Nsomething. And uh Susan uh was reading
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,something out of there was a Buddhist uh\NBible in Korea in in in a hotel room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.32,0:20:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a Bible there. Well, they\Nthey do have a Bible, but there's also a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddhist Bible sort of thing. So uh in\Nit she was reading that the Buddha was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,racked with pain as though his bones\Nwere broken and he was attacked by
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,demons. And she read that to me and inly\NI felt better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to be wrecked by demons and uh\Nfeel like all your bones are broken. So
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,those are just adventure stories neither\Nhere nor there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What I was really driving at is\Nout of power versus force, there seemed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to arise, and it bothered me at the\Ntime, a seeming duality, or at least one
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,could draw sort of a political uh\Nposition about it. Um, above 200 is that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,which is pro-life, supports life, and\Nthat which is true. Below 200 is that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,which is not true, does not support\Nlife. Everything that is venomous,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,hateful, selfish, greedy, destructive to\Nothers,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it that seemed to create a certain\Npolarity. So here is a work devoted to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,transcending polarities. And the work\Nitself seems to be bringing up a
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,polarity.\NUh you know, similar to good and evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there's above 200 and below 200. And\Nbelow 200, keep away from. Don't go out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and play with those kids that are below\N200, Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:22:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They have wicked greedy thoughts and uh\Nand are out to drag you down into a
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,street gang and get you tattooed and\Ndrugged up and hooked on heroin or
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,something and uh and they lure you into\Ncrime or evil or something. So uh it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,seemed to create that and that bothered\Nme and yet we went back over it and over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.96,0:22:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,again and of course those of you who are\Nfamiliar with the work of Dinesiology
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.03,0:22:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself know it is it is extremely\Ndefinite. There is nothing imaginary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.55,0:22:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If if science wants evidence-based um\Nwork, kinesiology is truly
