Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and or but about it. And it always gives\Nyou the same answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.91,0:22:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it sort of dawned on me uh sort\Nof dawned on me that that that first of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,all this scale is drawn a little\Nincorrectly. And I want to redraw it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.60,0:22:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,today. So\Nuh the other thing is that it's not
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,really two different worlds. What what\Nhappens is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Near the top of the scale at 1,00 you\Nhave the great avatars. So
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.72,0:23:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,there's the universal presence. There's\Nthe unmanifest
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.08,0:23:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,which becomes manifest as creation.\NCreation is continuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.15,0:23:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness as it interacts with\Nmatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,evolves as life and then life evolves up\Ninto higher and higher capacities
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,through evolution.\NTherefore, creation and evolution are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,one in the same thing. What science\Ncalls evolution is nothing but the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.24,0:23:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,unfolding of creation. As creation\Nunfolds, sequentially perception thinks
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.67,0:23:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it sees something happening. It's only\Nthe unfolding of evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So evolution is nothing but a\Ndemonstration of the fact that creation
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.88,0:24:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is continuous\Nwhich gets us away from the view of that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.24,0:24:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,God was uh God was around at the time of\NGenesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He um created uh the world and took off\Nand you don't see him again till you get
