Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.32,0:26:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh we're talking about when I first\Nwitnessed it went into that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.48,0:26:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The power that holds rock together,\Nsteel together, holds the planet
