Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.76,0:27:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So this infinite power then radiates\Nforth as the light of love. Huh? So
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.03,0:27:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,here's what we're actually seeing.\NHere's what we're actually seeing is
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.88,0:27:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that the top the the amount of love is\Nhigh at the top of the scale and becomes
