Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.52,0:27:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to draw you a new map of\Nconsciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.03,0:27:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,today. If any graphic artist, I'm sure\Nsomebody will figure out how to do this
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.91,0:27:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's doesn't look like kindergarten.\NBut anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.84,0:27:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so what we're seeing then is not good\Nand evil. This is not not two
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.24,0:27:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,contrasting either ors. You're seeing a\Ngreat deal of love, less and less and
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.12,0:28:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,less love and it diminishes. You're\Nlooking more like at a thermometer. You
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.00,0:28:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,see though there's only one variable.\NDon't forget to get beyond dualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.72,0:28:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to realize the error is\Nassuming that there's two variables.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.24,0:28:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one variable. We'll explain\Nthat there's either light. The only
