Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.03,0:28:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,things such as light and darkness.\NThere's only light. Light is either
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.72,0:28:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there or it's not there. And the light\Ncan be very very bright or it can be
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.88,0:28:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,very very dim. When it gets very very\Ndim, we say it's darkness. Darkness is
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.88,0:28:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,not a thing. You can't shine darkness\Ninto a closet. Shine me some darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.36,0:28:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It does no reality. The absence of\Nlight. So there's only one variable
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.00,0:28:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that's light.\NAnd in the scale of consciousness then
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.60,0:28:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,there's only one variable and that's\Nlove.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.60,0:28:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Infinite love makes you infinitely\Npowerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.67,0:28:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment of enlightenment which was\NJanuary 1065 or not the moment but
