Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.96,0:29:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,for many years.\NLet's just we recently out of curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.79,0:29:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was almost scared to ask that that was\Nthe one that had 500,000 resist. It was
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.96,0:29:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,a thought from the one at 500,000\Nresistance. A thought out of enormous
